{"tid":677044,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一種感覺","createTime":"2018-05-25T00:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T16:34:35.000Z","uid":124494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3de6f74e564d51277fbaecc76019bd1f0890d393","tid":677044,"uid":124494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T00:52:49.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過個腦突然有兩條電波咁 <br />\n一條係靜止 一條係幅好大好混亂咁<br />\n但只係會持續幾秒到一分鐘咁<br />\n好似下面圖同時出現咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/085042_ed48a80235d7f374d5de49cf2abeefde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F085042_ed48a80235d7f374d5de49cf2abeefde.png&h=c91731e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/085043_7a0397f48f38f92587d026512651bb97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F085043_7a0397f48f38f92587d026512651bb97.png&h=7dbc02b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時無啦啦會出現呢種感覺 發生緊果時會覺得有啲空虛同不安 覺得有啲奇妙 唔係中二病<br />\n有冇人都有試過同可以解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4790d2b0b99c7a4b3f7a984d3241fb708bc5d555","tid":677044,"uid":124494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}